2026-05-30T01:33:31.7126297Z Description:
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7127209Z libde265 is an open source implementation of the h.265 video codec. It is written from scratch and has a plain C API to enable a simple integration into other software.
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7128084Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7129407Z libde265 supports WPP and tile-based multithreading and includes SSE optimizations. The decoder supports all features of the Main and Main10 profile (HEVC-V1) and most profiles of HEVC-V2 (chroma 4:2:2, 4:4:4, monochrome, and bit depths up to 14 bits).
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7130976Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7131266Z libde265 is released under the LGPL, further information are available at
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7131856Z http://www.libde265.org
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7132221Z https://github.com/strukturag/libde265
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7132501Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7132721Z This PPA contains Ubuntu packages of the libde265 library.
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7133085Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7134039Z Plugins for the GStreamer framework, VLC and required dependencies are only provided for older versions of Ubuntu and are no longer maintained since the libde265 plugin is part of upstream GStreamer.
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7135118Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7135301Z The (old) GStreamer plugin source is available at
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7150862Z https://github.com/strukturag/gstreamer-libde265
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7160494Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7160721Z The VLC plugin source is available at
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7161236Z https://github.com/strukturag/vlc-libde265
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7161618Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7161782Z You can get sample Matroska streams from
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7162241Z http://www.libde265.org/downloads-videos/
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7162697Z http://www.divx.com/de/hevc
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7163100Z http://labs.divx.com/node/127909
2026-05-30T01:33:31.7163655Z More info: https://launchpad.net/~strukturag/+archive/ubuntu/libde265
