2026-05-30T01:33:37.8583302Z Description:
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8583852Z This PPA contains packages to add support for HEIC / HEIF and AVIF files.
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8584324Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8584771Z libheif is an ISO/IEC 23008-12:2017 HEIF and AVIF (AV1 Image File Format) file format decoder and encoder.
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8585384Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8586090Z HEIF and AVIF are new image file formats employing HEVC (h.265) or AV1 image coding, respectively, for the best compression ratios currently possible.
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8586902Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8587527Z libheif makes use of libde265 for HEIF image decoding and x265 for encoding. For AVIF, libaom, dav1d, or rav1e are used as codecs.
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8588250Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8588403Z libheif has support for decoding
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8588767Z - tiled images
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8589075Z - alpha channels
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8589368Z - thumbnails
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8589673Z - reading EXIF and XMP metadata
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8590225Z - reading the depth channel
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8590578Z - multiple images in a file
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8590993Z - image transformations (crop, mirror, rotate)
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8591438Z - overlay images
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8591957Z - plugin interface to add alternative codecs for additional formats (AVC, JPEG)
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8592965Z - decoding of files while downloading (e.g. extract image size before file has been completely downloaded)
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8593713Z - reading color profiles
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8594084Z - heix images (10 and 12 bit, chroma 4:2:2)
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8594372Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8594517Z The encoder supports:
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8594874Z - lossy compression with adjustable quality
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8595297Z - lossless compression
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8595620Z - alpha channels
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8595904Z - thumbnails
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8596205Z - save multiple images to a file
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8596580Z - save EXIF and XMP metadata
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8596954Z - writing color profiles
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8597297Z - 10 and 12 bit images
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8598044Z - monochrome images
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8598444Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8598731Z See https://github.com/strukturag/libheif for further information.
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8599165Z 
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8599437Z NOTE: You might also need to enable the PPA "strukturag/libde265",
2026-05-30T01:33:37.8600123Z so dependencies can be resolved.
